description:
Magnetometer Cable 

Description:
• 1 twisted pair with red polyethylene jacket
• Bronze wire braid over jacket of conductive polyethylene.
• Red PVC filler jacket, stainless steel wire braid, black polyethylene jacket

Construction:
• 1 twisted pair 4.5 mm stranded copper conductor 
• Insulated with polyethylene
• Core colours: blue and brown
• Wrapped with polyester tape
• Red polyethylene jacket 0.4mm bronze wire braid filled with conductive polyethylene
• Red PVC filler jacket
• 0.5mm sprung stainless steel wire braid
• Black polyethylene jacket

Physical Detail:
• Outer diameter 18.5 mm
• Weight in air 300 kg/km
• Weight in sea 220 kg/km
• Breaking strength 4 kN
• (Static) Minimum bending radius 180 mm
• (Dynamic) Minimum bending radius 270 mm
